    "description": "Signum Perfectum is a turn-based card game between two opponents that battle using constructed decks of 25 cards.<br><br>Defeat your enemies by casting magic upon them or protect yourself from their curses. Winning matches rewards in the form of new cards.<br><br>There are currenly 22 unique cards to collect, but more will come.<br><br>Each card has different sign that you need to &quot;catch&quot; during a match before card can be played. The bigger the level of card the bigger the power but also the harder is to catch the sign.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847930/extras/666323822990a346f026d367a401d016.poster.avif?t=1739992004\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847930/extras/666323822990a346f026d367a401d016.webm?t=1739992004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847930/extras/666323822990a346f026d367a401d016.mp4?t=1739992004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Level up your hero by casting cards to be able to use more powerful cards. There are four levels: Apprentice, Mage, High Mage and Archmage.<br><br>You can play single player quests and competitions or play against other players in multiplayer PvP matches.",
